                    class="inline-flex items-center bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/50 shadow-sm mb-10">
                    <span class="pulse-dot"></span>
                    <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-600">100% Secure • High Bitrate
