        <section class="py-32 px-4 bg-white">
            <div class="container mx-auto">
                <div class="text-center mb-24 animate-on-scroll">
                    <h2 class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Loved by Creators.</h2>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">See what our users are saying about BroqInsta.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
                    <div class="glass-card p-10 animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1 mb-6 text-amber-400 text-lg">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">"BroqInsta is hands down the fastest Instagram downloader I've ever used. The HD quality is incredible and it works every single time."</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-lg">S</div>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Sarah Mitchell</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Content Creator</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass-card p-10 animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1 mb-6 text-amber-400 text-lg">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">"I've tried dozens of downloaders and nothing compares. No ads, no popups, just pure speed. This is the tool every social media manager needs."</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 text-pink-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-lg">J</div>
                            <div>
